      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection inside and out. I\u2019m so excited for the next owner to get behind the wheel because it\u2019s a total gem. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
